@startuml SeqD_D05_View_Embryo_Development_Authorize_Phase

title SeqD_D05 — View Embryo Development & Authorize IVF Phase Transition

actor "Doctor" as DOC
participant "Embryology UI" as UI
participant "DoctorController" as CTRL
participant "DoctorService" as SVC
participant "AppDbContext" as DB
participant "NotificationService" as NOTIF

== View Embryo Development ==

DOC -> UI : Open patient profile → Embryology module
UI -> CTRL : GET /api/doctor/patients/{patientId}/embryos
CTRL -> SVC : GetEmbryoDataAsync(patientId, doctorId)
SVC -> DB : SELECT embryos + development entries\n+ lab technician notes\nWHERE cycle_id = activeIvfCycle
DB --> SVC : embryo list + data
SVC --> CTRL : embryo development data
CTRL --> UI : 200 OK — embryo data
UI --> DOC : Display IVF cycle summary:\ncell count, grade, morphology, lab notes

== Attach Clinical Note to Embryo ==

DOC -> UI : Select embryo → add clinical note\n(Transfer / Cryo / Discard + rationale)
UI -> CTRL : POST /api/doctor/embryos/{embryoId}/notes\n{instruction, rationale}
CTRL -> CTRL : Validate instruction and rationale fields

alt Fields missing
  CTRL --> UI : 400 Bad Request
  UI --> DOC : Highlight missing fields
end

CTRL -> SVC : AddEmbryoClinicalNoteAsync(embryoId, dto, doctorId)
SVC -> DB : INSERT EmbryoClinicalNote\n(immutable, timestamp, doctorId)
SVC -> NOTIF : NotifyLabTechnicianAsync(embryoId)
NOTIF --> SVC : lab technician notified
DB --> SVC : note saved
SVC --> CTRL : EmbryoClinicalNote
CTRL --> UI : 201 Created
UI --> DOC : Clinical note saved and visible to lab team

== Authorize IVF Phase Transition ==

DOC -> UI : Select "Authorize Phase Transition"\nChoose next phase
UI -> CTRL : POST /api/doctor/cycles/{cycleId}/authorize-phase\n{nextPhase, doctorId}
CTRL -> SVC : AuthorizePhaseTransitionAsync(cycleId, nextPhase, doctorId)
SVC -> DB : CHECK current phase conditions met

alt Conditions not met
  DB --> SVC : outstanding conditions
  SVC --> CTRL : 409 Conflict — conditions not met
  CTRL --> UI : 409 Conflict
  UI --> DOC : Show outstanding conditions to resolve
end

SVC -> DB : INSERT PhaseAuthorization\n(cycleId, nextPhase, doctorId, timestamp)
SVC -> DB : UPDATE IvfCycle SET currentPhase = nextPhase
SVC -> NOTIF : NotifyLabTechnicianAsync(cycleId, nextPhase)
NOTIF --> SVC : lab technician notified of new phase
DB --> SVC : phase advanced
SVC --> CTRL : updated cycle
CTRL --> UI : 200 OK
UI --> DOC : Cycle phase advanced — lab team notified

@enduml
